# Task 7 – Table Verification and Database Structure

## Project
Smart Library Request Workflow in ServiceNow

## Description

This task verifies the successful creation of the Book and Borrow Request tables and confirms that the database structure is ready for further development.

## Verification Performed

- Verified Book table (u_book)
- Verified Borrow Request table (u_borrow_request)
- Confirmed table names
- Confirmed tables are active
- Verified database structure

## Expected Outcome

The application database is validated and prepared for adding fields, relationships, and workflow configurations.

## Technologies Used

- ServiceNow
- System Definition
- Custom Tables
- Database Verification

## Status

Completed
